import { Avatar, Box, Button, Container, Grid, Paper, TextField, Typography } from '@mui/material'
import { useState } from 'react'

export default function Login() {

    const [text,setText] = useState({username:'', password:''})

    return (
        <Container align='center'>
            <Typography variant="h1" component="h1">LogIn</Typography>
            <Grid container>
                <Grid item xs={12}>
                    <Paper elevation={3}>
                        <Avatar style={{margin: "0 auto"}}>

                        </Avatar>
                        <Box>
                            <TextField type="username" onChange={(event) => {setText({...text, username: event.target.value})}}></TextField>
                            <TextField type="password" onChange={(event) => {setText({...text, password: event.target.value})}}></TextField>
                        </Box>

                        <Button variant = "contained"></Button>
                    </Paper>
                </Grid>
            </Grid>
        </Container>
        
    )
}
